description: Northern Minerals & Exploration Ltd. operates as a natural resource company in the United States. It produces oil and gas in central Texas; and explores for gold and silver in northern Nevada. The company holds interest in the J.E. Richey Lease project. The company was formerly known as Punchline Resources Ltd. and changed its name to Northern Minerals & Exploration Ltd. in August 2013. Northern Minerals & Exploration Ltd. was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Pleasant Grove, Utah.
